      <h3>2. Need for Ownership Flexibility</h3>
      <p>If you plan to sell or trade the excavator before the financing term ends, term loans offer more flexibility. Hire purchase agreements may have restrictions or penalties for early sale.</p>

      <h3>3. Strong Banking Relationships</h3>
